Has anyone seen this one before? Total SGC population of 3, none recognized by PSA.
I'd appreciate any information or comparable sales anyone can find!

There are 8 total that I know of, from my research on the variation I found that approximately 1 in 50 Piedmont 350's have the flaw. All of the variations also have a print flaw on the back and there is a correct front variation made from the same plate that has the same back flaw. I've seen 5 of those or approximately 1 in 75.
